# Rust build artefacts
/target/
**/*.rs.bk
Cargo.lock.bak

# IDE / editor scratch
/.idea/
/.vscode/
*.iml
*.swp
*.swo
.DS_Store

# Profiling / coverage outputs
/perf.data*
/flamegraph.svg
/coverage/
/tarpaulin-report.html
*.profraw
*.profdata

# Local-fix / CodeRabbit review artefacts. They embed local absolute
# paths and the user's name in metadata fields, so they must never be
# committed; the workflow regenerates them on every run.
/.claude/local-fix-*.jsonl
/.claude/local-fix-*.log

# Secrets — never commit these. CI runs gitleaks; this list is the
# defence-in-depth layer (per docs/plan.md §8.10).
*.pem
*.key
*.p12
*.pfx
.env
.env.*
!.env.example
secrets/
